d of America Award for Comedy/Variety (including talk) series]]<ref>{{cite web|title=2014 Writers Guild Awards Winners Announced |url=http://www.wga.org/content/default.aspx?id=5399 |work=Writers Guild of America |publisher=Writers Guild of America |accessdate=February 2, 2014 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160421153558/http://www.wga.org/content/default.aspx?id=5399 |archivedate=April 21, 2016}}</ref>\n| ''Jimmy Kimmel Live!''\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| [[Producers Guild of America Awards 2013|Producers Guild of America Award for Outstanding Producer of Live Entertainment & Talk Television]]<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.producersguild.org/news/151419/ |title = Nominations for Theatrical Motion Picture, Animated Theatrical Motion Picture and Long-Form TV |date = January 2, 2014 |work = [[Producers Guild of America]] |accessdate = January 2, 2014}}</ref>\n| ''Jimmy Kimmel Live!''\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| [[American Comedy Awards 2014|American Comedy Award for Best Late Night Talk Show]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://ew.com/article/2014/05/09/amy-poehler-seth-rogen-american-comedy-awards/|title = Amy Poehler, Seth Rogen win American Comedy Awards |work = Entertainment Weekly |date = May 9, 2014|first=Amber|last=Ray|accessdate = November 6, 2019}}</ref>\n| ''Jimmy Kimmel Live!''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Critics' Choice Television Award for Best Talk Show]]<ref>{{cite magazine |title = Critics' Choice TV Awards 2014: And the nominees are...|first=Ariana|last=Bacle|magazine = Entertainment Weekly |url=https://ew.com/article/2014/05/28/critics-choice-television-awards-nominees/|date = May 28, 2014 |accessdate = November 6, 2019}}</ref>\n| ''Jimmy Kimmel Live!''\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Variety Series]]<ref>{{cite news |url = https://www.nytimes.com/2014/07/11/arts/television/2014-emmy-nominations-game-of-thrones-true-detective-among-the-honored.html |title = 2014 Emmy Nominations: 'Breaking Bad,' 'True Detective' Among the Honored 